            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">49.304-1</ph> General.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2901e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2915e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            In a partial termination, the TCO shall limit the settlement to an adjustment of the fee, if any, and with the concurrence of the contracting office to a reduction in the estimated cost. The TCO shall adjust the fee as provided in <xref href="FAR-i1068269.dita#i1068269"
                        base="i1068269"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49.304-2</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1068286.dita#i1068286"
                        base="i1068286"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49.305</xref>, unless-</p>
					          <ol id="d2901e29" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2915e33" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The terminated portion is clearly severable from the balance of the contract; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2915e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Performance of the contract is virtually complete, or performance of any continued portion is only on subsidiary items or spare parts, or is otherwise not substantial.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2915e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            In the case of the exceptions in paragraph (a), the procedures in <xref href="FAR-i1068192.dita#i1068192"
                        base="i1068192"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49.302</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1068211.dita#i1068211"
                        base="i1068211"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49.303</xref> apply.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
